answersResultList.title: Somewhat Aquarius.
answersResultList.resultContent: A true Aquarius would visit the suburbs, laugh, and go away. If you're laughing at the burbs while living there, that makes you somewhat Aquarius. Your best ideas come through emotions and experiences, although the drive to road-test your beliefs is certainly an Aquarian trait. You like keeping busy, but with so many irons in the fire, you have no interest in leadership. And if you did find yourself in that role, you'd ask for input from your favorite team players and go with that. Who cares if this creates discord? You know who your friends are.

answersResultList.title: Mostly Aquarius.
answersResultList.resultContent: When you want isolation, you go somewhere wholesome and healing. When you want a healthy dose of humanity, you go where the action is. That's your Aquarian range of moods at work. While the things you want and don't want seem to change with the weather, your actual decisions are based on pure logic. This occasionally drives loved ones and colleagues crazy, especially when you act as if it gives you license to be in charge of everything. What they need to understand is that you only want to help, and this is the best way you know how.

answersResultList.title: Not very Aquarius.
answersResultList.resultContent: Your favorite place is alone in a crowd. You like the idea of humanity but have little use for people. While a true Aquarian might share this kind of detachment, your dislike for personal contact isn't very Aquarius. You obviously know a lot, and it pops into your mind by intuition rather than careful study or logical reasoning. Believing without seeking proof isn't very Aquarius, either. Based on the strength of your convictions and your removal from close interaction, you're happy to work alone. And if you come up with an idea for saving the world, you'll post it anonymously.

answersResultList.title: True Aquarius.
answersResultList.resultContent: The Water Bearer is an Air Sign, so it's totally Aquarian to seek open water, especially when there's a breeze. That's why your work and play styles are a mash-up of whatever works. Yes, you're pragmatic, but also visionary. The future is your kingdom, and it can be anything you want. You can be a little shy about letting them get too close, but the right person always wins your heart with smart words and bold ideas.
